{"tid":1139133,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"洗狗男不滿遭起底挑機　擬每七日殺一狗","createTime":"2019-05-05T04:42:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-05T05:37:28.000Z","uid":147376,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b8350d1fee8a47aeeb44fcfcb706c2130db63a88","tid":1139133,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T04:42:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://eastweek.my-magazine.me/main/36463\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Feastweek.my-magazine.me%2Fmain%2F36463&d=CFSJobiERGKWyjxxKHv2y5E%2BEEUKUWA%2FtqiTfwOa%2F%2FE%3D&h=1b7c5a1f\" target=\"_blank\">https://eastweek.my-magazine.me/main/36463</a><br />\n<br />\n自拍用洗衣機幫狗仔沖涼，最終攪死狗的冷血虐畜男，網名Jacky Lo，自將該虐畜照片放於社交網站上炫耀後，就遭一眾網民追擊圍攻，更成為報紙頭版。Jacky Lo看到自己的罪行被報道後，就於微博上稱自己身在澳門街，指要即時執拾細軟返回大陸避難。不過就有高登網民不齒其冷血，即時將他起底，指他是大陸腦殘富二代，並公開其個人資料於網上，資料包括其姓名、電話供應商及IP、住址、港澳通行證號碼，和他經常流連的地方。據悉，虐狗男叫羅X民，一九八九年出生，籍貫中國廣東，持雙程證來港，現居於屯門。<br />\n<br />\n惟Jacky Lo面對全城圍插仍不知悔改，今日(九月十三日)疑不滿遭起底向高登網民挑機，於自己的社交網站上寫道：「高登咁鍾意起底，我就同你玩個遊戲。我手上共有六隻流浪狗，我七日問你一個問題，如果答錯我就殺死一隻狗，答對就放一隻狗。狗的生死就睇你啦！」又鬧爆公開資料的高登網站，指他們誤導網民和媒體，行為幼稚、無知、可笑，並暗示起底資料有誤，叫他們不要強出頭。但網民就再三確認其資料屬實，更向面書、新浪微博及入境處查證，其訊號發出的IP為同一地址，而且沒有出境紀錄，即Jacky Lo從沒有離開香港。另外，有網民進行電子報案，冀警方可盡快將Jacky Lo拘捕，以免有更多無辜小狗受害，惟Jacky Lo今日約四時許再度更新微博，寫道：「不評論、不發表、隔山觀虎斗。」"},{"pid":"4d0e25a8c625ccff8164c5dd6a70847030a42b9d","tid":1139133,"uid":175661,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T04:44:29.000Z","msg":"玩個遊戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢係咪以為自己好型?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d4f01c3545bbab551eb6107da40784408c5074d","tid":1139133,"uid":137159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T04:46:21.000Z","msg":"有地址有名佢唔怕人報警拉柒佢，仲玩咁大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08db757b058dc179d3d5add17cdab777e4ed8d95","tid":1139133,"uid":114217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T04:47:38.000Z","msg":"回帶西"},{"pid":"b8eacecd69a07b07150f2690494cd6a0236442d0","tid":1139133,"uid":213637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T04:57:31.000Z","msg":"好似幾年前嘅新聞黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6f77c61ebc6d19cfd29e978772bab00a98f74bf","tid":1139133,"uid":237562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T04:58:56.000Z","msg":"dog kill dog"},{"pid":"2beae13a73cb055bdec573dc3ef11fe354934086","tid":1139133,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b8eacecd69a07b07150f2690494cd6a0236442d0","tid":1139133,"uid":213637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T04:57:31.000Z","msg":"好似幾年前嘅新聞黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T04:59:36.000Z","msg":"完全冇曬下文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a4a70b6ce2f2018fb595944eaacd92712922fc2","tid":1139133,"uid":16567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T05:01:13.000Z","msg":"最後件事點？"},{"pid":"4635e651508583155f8e50b706c82d0a4ab932c7","tid":1139133,"uid":211461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T05:37:28.000Z","msg":"2014年9月13日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}